text: How do I print current year in HubL? I have tried {{ pprint|year }} and {{ now.year }}. None of them seem to work?
No worries. It works everywhere btw, in the frontend as well

I am thinking the module came from somewhere in the marketplace (I didn't make the site) and was deprecated or something and now exists only as "legacy". It's the first time this happens and I really couldn't find it. Not a huge deal, I will actually create a new module based on this one's functionalities, but this was strange hehe
